title: 082: Future of MindPump, Elevation Masks, Deadlifts & Squats and Quick Bulking
description: Sal, Adam & Justin love answering your questions (Instagram @mindpump). In this episode they answer PumpHead questions about the future of MindPump, training with elevation masks, conventional vs. sumo deadlifts, high bar vs low bar squats and how to pack on 15 pounds fast.
